od.%20Any%20payment%20overages%20resulting%20from%20an%20employee%20being%20paid%20for%20a%20scheduled%20shift%20from%20November%2018%20through%20November%2024%20that%20they%20did%20not%20report%20to%20work%20for%C2%A0will%20not%20be%20required%20to%20be%20paid%20back%2C%20the%20documents%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Starbucks%20partner%20in%20the%20South%20said%20their%20manager%20told%20them%20on%20Monday%20that%20employees%20who%20had%20paid%20time%20off%20planned%20for%20the%20affected%20weeks%20won't%20be%20paid%20for%20that%20time%20until%20the%20outage%20has%20been%20fixed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20%26quot%3Bpotentially%20very%20bad%20for%20some%20partners%20taking%20vacation%20around%20the%20holidays%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20partner%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20Starbucks%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20company%20is%20working%20to%20ensure%20its%20partners%20are%20paid%20for%20their%20hours%20worked%20with%20limited%20disruption%2C%20and%20indicated%20the%20outage%20has%20not%20disrupted%20customer-facing%20technology%20or%20service%20in%20any%20of%20its%20locations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBlue%20Yonder's%20software%20is%20also%20used%20by%20major%20grocery%20store%20chains%20and%20Fortune%20500%20firms%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2F2024%2F11%2F24%2Fbusiness%2Fransomware-attack-blue-yonder%2Findex.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECNN%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESimilar%20cyber%20attacks%20have%20previously%20left%20companies%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstaff-at-sony-pictures-are-using-pens-and-paper-after-a-massive-hack-2014-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESony%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fcar-dealerships-cyberattack-cdk-outage-3f7c81f6be0e212172b33cdc9f49feba%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecar%20dealerships%3C%2Fa%3E%20across%20America%20using%20pen%20and%20paper%20for%20admin