d%20he's%20seen%20families%20become%20closer%20when%20the%20will%20is%20shared%20in%20advance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20context%2C%20the%20most%20recent%20Federal%20Reserve%20data%20collected%20from%202016%20to%202019%20indicates%20the%20average%20American%20inheritance%20is%20%2446%2C200%20%E2%80%94%20much%20less%20than%20the%20%2410%20million%20Buffett's%20late%20wife%20left%20for%20her%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBuffett%20also%20shared%20details%20about%20the%20unanimous%20vote%20provision%20he%20included%20in%20his%20will.%20The%20clause%20requires%20his%20three%20children%20to%20approve%20all%20donation%20decisions%20after%20his%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20explained%20that%20my%20children%20will%20forever%20be%20besieged%20with%20earnest%20requests%20from%20very%20sincere%20friends%20and%20others%2C%26quot%3B%20Buffett%20wrote%20in%20the%20letter.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Buffett%20said%20his%20children%20will%20forever%20be%20regarded%20as%20%26quot%3Btargets%20of%20opportunity%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20and%20them%20saying%20no%20to%20donation%20pleas%20won't%20always%20make%20the%20requests%20go%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBuffett%20said%20the%20unanimous%20provision%20provides%20%26quot%3Ban%20immediate%26quot%3B%20and%20definitive%20response%20to%20grant-seekers%2C%20allowing%20them%20to%20say%2C%20for%20example%2C%20%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20something%20that%20would%20ever%20receive%20my%20brother's%20consent.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBuffett%20said%20the%20clause%20isn't%20a%20remedy%20for%20all%20families%2C%20as%20it%20wouldn't%20work%20for%20a%20large%20group%20of%20children%2C%20and%20it%20doesn't%20remove%20the%20children's%20responsibility%20to%20choose%20where%20to%20donate%20billions.%20Still%2C%20he%20said%20it%20would%20help%20improve%20their%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBuffett%20remains%20one%20of%20the%20wealthiest%20people%20in%20the%20world%20with%20a%20%24150%20billion%20net%20worth%2C%20Forbes%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.forbe