20on%20'The%20Office%2C'%20and%20'The%20Office'%20became%20one%20of%20the%20most%20commercially%20and%20creatively%20successful%20shows%20that's%20ever%20existed%20in%20Hollywood.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGetting%20writing%20pointers%20from%20%26quot%3BThe%20Office%26quot%3B%20showrunner%20Greg%20Daniels%20proved%20to%20be%20life-changing%20for%20growing%20Schur's%20skillset%20and%20opening%20the%20doors%20for%20his%20next%20move.%20When%20he%20joined%20forces%20with%20Daniels%20as%20cocreators%20of%20%26quot%3BParks%20and%20Recreation%2C%26quot%3B%20his%20association%20with%20an%20already%20successful%20showrunner%20cleared%20many%20of%20the%20traditional%20barriers%20to%20getting%20noticed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20normal%20process%20of%20making%20your%20first%20show%20is%20incredibly%20difficult%2C%20and%20you%20have%20to%20jump%20over%20all%20these%20hurdles%20and%20get%20incredibly%20lucky%2C%26quot%3B%20Schur%20said.%20%26quot%3BBeing%20associated%20with%20that%20show%20and%20learning%20how%20to%20write%20from%20Greg%20Daniels%20meant%20that%20I%20got%20the%20enormous%20benefits%20out%20of%20my%20very%20first%20job%20that%2099.9%25%20of%20all%20people%20who%20ever%20become%20writers%20just%20don't%20get%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20continued.%20%26quot%3BI%20skipped%20the%20line.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20one%20thing%20to%20get%20an%20opportunity%3B%20it's%20another%20to%20hold%20on%20to%20your%20success.%20Though%20Schur%20acknowledged%20that%20being%20in%20the%20right%20place%20at%20the%20right%20time%20allowed%20him%20to%20operate%20from%20a%20place%20of%20%26quot%3Brelative%20comfort%20and%20luxury%26quot%3B%20for%20most%20of%20his%20career%2C%20navigating%20a%20notoriously%20cutthroat%20industry%20like%20Hollywood%20still%20requires%20a%20level%20of%20self-preservation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThrough%20it%20all%2C%20he's%20emerged%20with%20a%20reputation%20as%20a%20nice%20guy%20who%20makes%20television%20that's%20literally%20about%20how%20people%20should%2