%2Fnews%2Fravi-shastri-recalls-a-heartfelt-request-made-by-virat-kohli-in-2015-related-to-anushka-sharma%2Farticleshow%2F115669012.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F115669012.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EDuring%20the%202015%20Australia%20tour%2C%20Virat%20Kohli%20sought%20permission%20from%20then-coach%20Ravi%20Shastri%20to%20have%20his%20girlfriend%2C%20Anushka%20Sharma%2C%20join%20him%20despite%20team%20regulations.%20Shastri%20pulled%20some%20strings%2C%20and%20Anushka's%20presence%20seemingly%20boosted%20Kohli's%20performance.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fravi-shastri-recalls-a-heartfelt-request-made-by-virat-kohli-in-2015-related-to-anushka-sharma%2Farticleshow%2F115669012.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Clashes%20At%20Udaipur%20Palace%20Gates%20Over%20New%20Maharana's%20Face-Off%20With%20Cousin%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUdaipur%20witnessed%20a%20row%20in%20the%20erstwhile%20royal%20family%20today%20after%20the%20coronation%20of%20BJP%20MLA%20Vishvaraj%20Singh%20Mewar%20as%20the%2077th%20Maharana%20of%20Mewar.%20A%20stand-off%20with%20his%20cousin%20Dr%20Lakshay%20Raj%20Singh%20Mewar%20followed%20at%20the%20gates%20of%20the%20historic%20city%20palace%2C%20after%20Mr%20Singh%20was%20refused%20entry%20into%20the%20palace%2C%20which%20is%20now%20run%20by%20a%20trust%20managed%20by%20his%20cousin%20and%20uncle%20Shreeji%20Arvind%20Singh%20Mewar.%20The%20row%20it%20sparked%20escalated%20as%20the%20day%20progressed.%20Post-10%20pm%2C%20the%20MLA's%20supporters%20started%20throwing%20stones%20and%20attempted%20to%20storm%20the%20palace%20gates.%20Others%20are%20retaliating%20from%20inside%20the%20palace.%20Hectic%20visuals%20from%20palace%20gates%20shows%20stones%20landing%20from%20both%20sides%2C%20Three%20people%20have%20been%20injured%20and%20the%20police%20are%20trying%20to%20control%20the%20mob.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReports%20say%20Vishvaraj%20Singh%20has%20been%20standing%20with%20his%20supporters%20at%20the%20spot%20for%20the%20last%205%20hours.%20The%20district%20administration%20has%20now%20decided%20to%20intervene.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVishvaraj%20Singh%20--%20the%20BJP%20MLA%20from%20Rajsamand%20from%20where%20his%20wife%20Mahima%20Kumari%20is%20the%20sitting%20MP%20--%20was%20formally%20declared%20the%20heir%20to%20the%20Mewar%20dynasty%20at%20a%20traditional%20coronation%20ceremony%20in%20the%20historic%20Chittorgarh%20fort%2012%20days%20after%20the%20death%20of%20his%20father%20Mahendra%20Singh%20Mewar.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20coronation%20ceremony%2C%20conducted%20by%20priests%20who%20performed%20pujas%20and%20did%20a%20havan%2C%20saw%20Vishwaraj's%20raj%20tilak%20done%20by%20an%20erstwhile%20noble%20who%20slashed%20his%20finger%20on%20a%20sword%20and%20anointed%20him%20in%20blood.%20This%20is%20a%20tradition%20that%20goes%20back%20hundreds%20of%20years%20in%20the%20Mewar%20dynasty%2C%20which%20traces%20its%20lineage%20back%20to%20Bappa%20Rawal%20in%20the%208th%20Century.%20Its%20most%20famous%20royal%20was%20Rana%20Pratap%2C%20who%20fought%20the%20Mughals%20in%20the%20battle%20of%20Haldi%20Ghati.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20symbolic%20coronation%2C%20Mr%20Singh%20had%20decided%20to%20take%20the%20blessings%20from%20family%20deities%20--%20the%20Dhooni%20mata%20temple%20inside%20the%20city%20palace%20and%20the%20Ekling%20Shiv%20temple%20about%2050%20kilometres%20from%20Udaipur.%C2%A0But%20since%20both%20temples%20are%20run%20by%20the%20trust%2C%20he%20was%20denied%20entry%20into%20the%20city%20palace.%C2%A0The%20administration%20had%20tried%20to%20persuade%20the%20Museum%20Trust%20to%20allow%20not%20the%20entire%20procession%2C%20but%20a%20few%20erstwhile%20nobles%20to%20accompany%20Vishwaraj%20Singh%20into%20the%20palace%20for%20darshan.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnticipating%20trouble%2C%20the%20police%20had%20set%20up%20barricades%20and%20deployed%20additional%20personnel%20in%20the%20area%20around%20the%20city%20palace%20gates.%20But%20when%20Mr%20Singh%20was%20denied%20entry%20into%20the%20palace%2C%20his%20enraged%20supporters%20broke%20barricades%20and%20tried%20to%20get%20close%20to%20the%20city%20palace%20gates.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20situation%20that%20we%20see%20today%20is%20unfortunate%2C%26quot%3B%20Vishvaraj%20Singh%20told%20media%20persons.%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20grateful%20for%20your%20support.%20On%20one%20side%20is%20properties%2C%20but%20there%20are%20also%20traditions%20where%20we%20seek%20blessings.%20This%20is%20wrong%20as%20far%20as%20traditions%20and%20society%20norms%20are%20concerned%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20generation%20of%20Mewar%20royals%20have%20been%20involved%20in%20a%20legal%20dispute%20over%20palaces%2C%20temples%20and%20forts%20that%20are%20now%20run%20and%20managed%20by%20nine%20trusts.%20All%20these%20trusts%20are%20handled%20by%20the%20uncle%20and%20cousin%20of%20Vishvaraj%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarly%20this%20morning%2C%20the%20Maharana%20Mewar%20Charitable%20Trust%20published%20in%20the%20local%20newspapers%20that%20they%20would%20not%20allow%20anyone%20to%20enter%20the%20trust%20premises%20as%20they%20anticipated%20that%20this%20could%20be%20done%20with%20an%20intention%20to%20trespass%20on%20and%20damage%20trust%20properties.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20dispute%20goes%20back%20to%201984%2C%20when%20the%20former%20Maharana%20of%20Mewar%20Bhagwat%20Singhji%20made%20his%20younger%20son%20Arvind%20Singh%20the%20director%20of%20the%20trusts%2C%20effectively%20ousting%20the%20elder%20son%20Mahendra%20Singh%20from%20the%20royal%20properties.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20stand-off%20continues%20in%20Udaipur%2C%20this%20is%20a%20royal%20row%20that's%20going%20to%20echo%20in%20the%20City%20of%20Lakes%20for%20some%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732556640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2F3u1e7f6_udaipur-palace-violence_625x300_25_November_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fclashes-at-udaipur-palace-gates-over-new-maharanas-face-off-with-cousin-7104723%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Udaipur%20witnessed%20a%20row%20in%20the%20erstwhile%20royal%20family%20today%20after%20the%20coronation%20of%20BJP%20MLA%20Vishvaraj%20Singh%20Mewar%20as%20the%2077th%20Maharana%20of%20Mewar.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Esha%20Deol's%20birthday%20post%20for%20Celina%20Jaitly%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732555999000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-115667916%2Cimgsize-43668.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fesha-deol-shares-a-warm-birthday-post-for-celina-jaitly-love-love-and-only-love-for-you-always%2Farticleshow%2F115667916.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F115667916.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ECelina%20Jaitly%20celebrated%20her%2043rd%20birthday%20amidst%20the%20Austrian%20Alps%20with%20her%20family.%20Esha%20Deol%2C%20her%20'No%20Entry'%20co-star%2C%20shared%20a%20heartfelt%20birthday%20wish%20on%20Instagram%2C%20reminiscing%20about%20their%20time%20on%20set.%20Jaitly%20expressed%20her%20preference%20for%20intimate%20family%20celebrations%20over%20lavish%20parties%2C%20finding%20greater%20joy%20in%20spending%20her%20special%20day%20with%20loved%20ones.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22en