ress%20hard%20-%20the%20party's%20score%20has%20dropped%20from%2011%20to%20five.%20The%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20faction%20of%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20Uddhav%20has%20got%20six%20seats%20and%20Sharad%20Pawar's%20NCP%20faction%20got%20two.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20the%2038%20seats%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20increased%20its%20tally%20from%2011%20in%202019%20to%2014.%20The%20Shiv%20Sena%20of%20Eknath%20Shinde%20has%20won%20six%20seats%20and%20Ajit%20Pawar's%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20two%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20the%20remaining%20three%20seats%2C%20Samajwadi%20Party%20got%20two%20and%20Asaduddin%20Owaisi's%20AIMIM%20got%20just%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20outcome%20indicates%20that%20the%20clerics%20failed%20to%20dominate%20the%20collective%20decision%20of%20the%20Muslim%20community%20-%20a%20situation%20that%20helped%20the%20BJP%20strengthen%20its%20allegations%20of%20%26quot%3Bvote%20jihad%26quot%3B%20or%20consolidation%20of%20Muslim%20votes%20against%20the%20Mahayuti.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDenying%20Opposition%20allegations%20of%20polarisation%2C%20senior%20BJP%20leader%20Vinay%20Sahasrabuddhe%20said%20all%20communities%20are%20included%20in%20the%20slogan%20%26quot%3BEk%20hain%20toh%20safe%20hain%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BPeople%20did%20not%20fall%20prey%20to%20the%20politics%20of%20appeasement%20and%20polarisation%20of%20the%20MVA%2C%20and%20came%20together%20to%20vote%20for%20development.%20All%20communities%20are%20included%20in%20our%20'Ek%20hain%20toh%20safe%20hain'%20mantra%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20was%20no%20place%20for%20appeasement%2C%20people%20here%20look%20at%20development%20and%20benefits%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Salim%20Sarang%2C%20the%20president%20of%20the%20Muslim%20Welfare%20Association.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20big%20Muslim%20names%20who%20lost%20were%20NCP's%20Nawab%20Malik%20and%20Zeeshan%20Siddiqui%20as%20well%20as%20Congress's%20Arif%20Naseem%20Khan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EData%20indicates%20that%20while%20the%20support%20of%20the%20Muslim%20community%20helped%20the%20MVA%20win%20a%20big%20victory%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20held%20in%20May%2C%20what%20went%20against%20them%20in%20the%20Assembly%20polls%20were%20low%20enthusiasm%2C%20divided%20votes%20and%20communal%20polarization%20in%20some%20seats.%20In%20some%20seats%2C%20the%20presence%20of%20multiple%20Muslim%20candidates%20split%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20in%20Aurangabad%20East%2C%20AIMIM%20state%20chief%20and%20former%20MP%20Imtiaz%20Jaleel%20lost%20to%20the%20BJP's%20Atul%20Save%20by%202%2C161%20votes.%20VBA's%20Afsar%20Khan%20(6%2C507%20votes)%20and%20SP's%20Abdul%20Gaffar%20Syed%20(5%2C943%20votes)%20split%20the%20Muslim%20vote%20in%20the%20seat%2C%20ensuring%20Jaleel's%20defeat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20seat%20AIMIM%20won%20was%20in%20Muslim-dominated%20Malegaon%20Central%2C%20where%20its%20candidate%20Mufti%20Ismail%2C%20the%20sitting%20MLA%2C%20won%20by%20just%20162%20votes-the%20lowest%20margin%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20in%20Bhiwandi%20West%2C%20Mahesh%20Chaugule%20of%20the%20BJP%20defeated%20Riyaz%20Azmi%20of%20the%20SP%20by%2031%2C293%20votes%20as%20Muslims%20also%20divided%20their%20votes%20between%20AIMIM's%20Waris%20Pathan%20(15%2C800%20votes)%20and%20Independent%20Vilas%20Patil%20(31%2C579%20votes).%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732552260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2F6q9eba9g_bjp-celebration_625x300_08_October_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fthe-impact-of-muslim-votes-on-maharashtra-assembly-election-results-7104475%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20sweep%20of%20the%20ruling%20alliance%20in%20Maharashtra%20has%20been%20widely%20attributed%20to%20the%20welfare%20programmes%20of%20the%20Eknath%20Shinde%20government.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22a