B%22title%22%3A%22What's%20Behind%20The%20Alarming%20Rise%20In%20Crimes%20By%20Young%20Men%20In%20Madhya%20Pradesh%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EYoungsters%20in%20the%20age%20cohort%2020-30%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh's%20major%20cities%20are%20increasingly%20committing%20heinous%20crimes%20to%20sustain%20relationship%20and%20maintain%20a%20high-end%20lifestyle%2C%20shows%20data%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20three%20years%2C%20police%20records%20and%20court%20documents%20have%20revealed%20a%20significant%20surge%20in%20such%20cases%2C%20primarily%20in%20urban%20centers%20like%20Bhopal%2C%20Indore%2C%20Jabalpur%2C%20and%20Gwalior.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Bhopal%20district%20court%20data%2C%20the%20majority%20of%20offenders%20in%20murder%20and%20rape%20cases%20belong%20to%20the%2020-30%20age%20group%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202022%3A%2044%20convicted%20for%20murder%2C%2011%20for%20rape%3Cbr%3E%5CnIn%202023%3A%2046%20convicted%20for%20murder%2C%2018%20for%20rape%3Cbr%3E%5CnTill%20June%202024%3A%2024%20convicted%20for%20murder%2C%208%20for%20rape%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20take%20the%20case%20of%2027-year-old%20Sheetal%20Kaushal%20and%20her%20boyfriend%20Vinod%2C%20an%20MBA%20student.%20On%20May%2015%2C%202024%2C%20a%20vacation%20to%20Manali%20turned%20tragic%20when%20Vinod%20allegedly%20killed%20Sheetal%20in%20their%20hotel%20room%20following%20an%20argument%20over%20lifestyle%20expenses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20grim%20incident%20unfolded%20on%20Valentine's%20Day%20in%202023%20when%2020-year-old%20Raunak%20from%20Bhopal%20allegedly%20killed%20his%20mother%20for%20refusing%20to%20give%20him%20money%20to%20buy%20an%20expensive%20gift%20for%20his%20girlfriend%20and%20to%20attend%20a%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20Neeraj%20Bhavnani%2C%2030%2C%20was%20caught%20in%20Bhopal's%20New%20Market%20while%20shopping%20with%20his%20girlfriend%20using%20stolen%20money.%20He%20had%20reportedly%20committed%20multiple%20thefts%2C%20including%20chain%20snatching%2C%20to%20fund%20his%20partner's%20shopping%20sprees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20officials%20say%20these%20crimes%20often%20involve%20first-time%20offenders%2C%20making%20investigations%20challenging.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20the%20trend%2C%20Bhopal%20Police%20Commissioner%2C%20Harinarayan%20Chari%20Mishra%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BMost%20offenders%20are%20from%20other%20cities%2C%20drawn%20to%20urban%20areas%20by%20the%20lure%20of%20a%20better%20lifestyle.%20They%20fall%20into%20bad%20company%20or%20give%20in%20to%20pressures%2C%20leading%20to%20serious%20crimes.%20Families%20and%20educational%20institutions%20need%20to%20monitor%20such%20behavior%20closely.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdvocate%20Rajendra%20Upadhyay%2C%20a%20district%20prosecution%20officer%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BMany%20engineering%20and%20medical%20students%20are%20committing%20crimes%20to%20sustain%20relationships%20or%20maintain%20a%20luxurious%20lifestyle.%20This%20age%20group%2C%2018-30%2C%20is%20particularly%20vulnerable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPsychologists%2C%20too%2C%20are%20sounding%20the%20alarm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSocial%20media's%20influence%20and%20the%20pressure%20to%20project%20a%20lavish%20image%20are%20harming%20today's%20youth.%20Financial%20literacy%20and%20emotional%20intelligence%20are%20critical%20lessons%20that%20parents%20and%20schools%20must%20impart%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr%20Vinay%20Mishra%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20rise%20in%20such%20cases%2C%20law%20enforcement%20agencies%20are%20calling%20for%20collaborative%20efforts%20between%20families%2C%20schools%2C%20and%20communities%20to%20guide%20young%20individuals%20and%20deter%20them%20from%20criminal%20activities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20authorities%20strive%20to%20address%20this%20growing%20issue%2C%20these%20incidents%20underline%20the%20urgent%20need%20for%20societal%20introspection%20and%20a%20stronger%20focus%20on%20values%20and%20emotional%20well-being.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732547940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Flsvkksj8_neeraj-_625x300_25_November_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmajority-offenders-for-serious-crime-in-madhya-pradesh-in-20-30-age-group-data-7103860%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Youngsters%20in%20the%20age%20cohort%2020-30%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh's%20major%20cities%20are%20increasingly%20committing%20heinous%20crimes%20to%20sustain%20relationship%20and%20maintain%20a%20high-end%20lifestyle%2C%20shows%20data.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmajority-offenders-for-serious-crime-in-madhya-pradesh-in-20-30-age-group-data-7103860%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Who%20Is%20Vaibhav%20Suryavanshi%3F%2013-Year-Old%20Picked%20By%20RR%20For%20Rs%201.10%20Crore%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EVaibhav%20Suryavanshi%2C%20a%2013-year-old%20cricketer%20from%20Bihar%2C%20entered%20history%20books%20as%20he%20became%20the%20youngest-ever%20player%20to%20be%20bought%20at%20an%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL)%20auction.%20Suryavanshi%2C%20the%20youngest%20player%20to%20register%2C%20was%20sold%20to%20Rajasthan%20Royals%20for%20Rs%201.10%20crore%20on%20Day%202%20of%20the%20IPL%202025%20Mega%20Auction%20on%20Monday%20in%20Jeddah%2C%20Saudi%20Arabia.%20RR%20were%20involved%20in%20a%20bidding%20war%20for%20the%20player%20with%20Delhi%20Capitals%2C%20who%20pulled%20out%20after%20the%20former%20bid%20Rs%201.10%20crore%20for%20the%20teenager.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20is%20Vaibhav%20Suryavanshi%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%202011-born%20started%20to%20show%20his%20cricketing%20talent%20at%20the%20tender%20age%20of%204.%20Vaibhav's%20father%20Sanjeev%20noticed%20his%20passion%20and%20decided%20to%20build%20a%20small%20playing%20area%20for%20him%20in%20the%20backyard%20of%20the%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20age%20of%209%2C%20Vaibhav's%20father%20enrolled%20him%20in%20a%20cricket%20academy%20in%20the%20nearby%20town%20of%20Samastipur.%20It%20didn't%20take%20long%20for%20people%20around%20him%20to%20notice%20that%20Vaibhav%20was%20well%20ahead%20of%20his%20age%20in%20terms%20of%20cricketing%20talent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20practising%20for%20two-and-a-half%20years%20there%2C%20I%20gave%20Under-16%20trials%20for%20the%20Vijay%20Merchant%20Trophy%2C%26quot%3B%20Vaibhav%20said%20in%20a%20chat%20with%20the%20Times%20of%20India.%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20on%20standby%20due%20to%20my%20age.%20By%20God's%20grace%2C%20I%20started%20coaching%20under%20Manish%20Ojha%20sir%2C%20a%20former%20Ranji%20player.%20He%20has%20taught%20me%20a%20lot%20and%20whatever%20I%20am%20today%2C%20it%20is%20because%20of%20him.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVaibhav%20was%20only%2012%20years%20old%20when%20he%20played%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Vinoo%20Mankad%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F41126-mulwantrai-himatlal-mankad-playerprofile%5C%22%3EVinoo%20Mankad%3C%2Fa%3E%20Trophy%20for%20Bihar%2C%20scoring%20around%20400%20runs%20in%20just%20five%20matches.%20It%20didn't%20take%20him%20long%20to%20rise%20through%20the%20ranks%20in%20Bahar%20Cricket%2C%20making%20heads%20turn%20wherever%20he%20went.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVaibhav%2C%20who%20debuted%20for%20Bihar%20at%20the%20tender%20age%20of%2012%2C%20has%20quickly%20made%20a%20name%20for%20himself%20in%20the%20cricketing%20world.%20His%20recent%20achievement%2C%20a%20blistering%2058-ball%20century%20against%20the%20Australian%20U-19%20team%20in%20a%20four-day%20game%20in%20Chennai%2C%20solidified%20his%20position%20as%20a%20rising%20star.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVaibhav%20wa%20a%20part%20of%20the%20India%20B%20U-19%20team%20for%20an%20Under-19%20quadrangular%20series%20in%20Mulapadu%2C%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20in%20November%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20f