cal%20dialect%20and%20using%20video%20formats%20to%20explain%20them%2C%20they%20are%20ensuring%20that%20the%20tribal%20population%20is%20not%20left%20out%20of%20important%20decisions%20that%20affect%20their%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20COVID%2C%20when%20hyperlocal%20information%20became%20crucial%2C%20Nitesh%20and%20his%20team%20worked%20tirelessly%20to%20ensure%20the%20community%20stayed%20informed.%20%E2%80%9CI%20would%20take%20the%20WHO%20reports%2C%20translate%20them%20into%20Hindi%2C%20and%20then%20our%20team%20members%20would%20further%20translate%20them%20into%20our%20local%20dialect%2C%20Pawari.%20By%20the%20time%20the%20content%20was%20available%20in%20Marathi%2C%20we%20already%20had%20the%20information%20ready%20for%20our%20community%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Nitesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAadiwasi%20Janjagruti%20has%20successfully%20addressed%20several%20local%20issues%2C%20making%20a%20tangible%20difference%20in%20the%20community.%20One%20such%20case%20involved%20a%20woman%20whose%20nine%20goats%20died%20from%20poisoning.%20While%20the%20loss%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20considered%20significant%20enough%20by%20mainstream%20news%20outlets%2C%20it%20devastated%20her%20livelihood%20and%20affected%20the%20entire%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAadiwasi%20Janjagruti%20raised%20awareness%20about%20the%20issue%2C%20bringing%20it%20to%20the%20attention%20of%20local%20authorities%2C%20and%20the%20woman%20ultimately%20received%20compensation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20instance%2C%20the%20team%20worked%20relentlessly%20to%20highlight%20a%20road%20construction%20project%20that%20had%20been%20stalled%20for%20years.%20Their%20videos%20drew%20attention%20to%20the%20issue%2C%20and%20the%20road%20was%20finally%20completed%20in%202022.%20The%20villagers%20were%20so%20proud%20of%20the%20outcome%20that%20they%20decided%20to%20name%20the%20road%20after%20Aadiwasi%20Janjagruti.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Dhadgaon%2C%20a%20bridge%20project%20had%20been%20stuck%20in%20limbo%20f