0and%20healthcare%20experts%20responded%2C%20stating%20that%20such%20claims%20lack%20high-quality%20evidence%20to%20support%20them.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConsequently%2C%20Mr%20Sidhu%20issued%20a%20clarification%2C%20stating%20that%20his%20wife's%20fight%20against%20cancer%20involved%20surgeries%2C%20chemotherapy%2C%20hormonal%20and%20targeted%20therapies%2C%20a%20strict%20diet%20plan%2C%20and%20determination%20to%20combat%20the%20disease.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20neem%20leaves%2C%20turmeric%2C%20and%20intermittent%20fasting%20may%20assist%20in%20the%20supportive%20management%20of%20cancer%2C%20there%20is%20no%20scientific%20evidence%20to%20support%20the%20effectiveness%20of%20apple%20cider%20vinegar%20and%20lemon%20in%20cancer%20management.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20there%20is%20no%20medical%20consensus%20or%20scientific%20evidence%20to%20substantiate%20the%20claim%20that%20neem%20leaves%2C%20turmeric%2C%20apple%20cider%20vinegar%2C%20lemon%20water%2C%20or%20intermittent%20fasting%20can%20cure%20cancer.%20Hence%2C%20the%20claim%20made%20in%20the%20post%20is%20MISLEADING.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20it%20is%20important%20to%20note%20that%20Mr%20Sidhu%2C%20in%20the%20same%20press%20conference%2C%20emphasized%20the%20indispensable%20role%20of%20the%20healthcare%20system%20and%20accessible%20medical%20treatments%20in%20managing%20critical%20illnesses%20like%20cancer.%20He%20shared%20his%20wife's%20journey%2C%20highlighting%20the%20significant%20contribution%20of%20government%20hospitals%20to%20her%20treatment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESidhu%20also%20advocated%20for%20a%20holistic%20approach%20to%20health%2C%20underscoring%20the%20importance%20of%20a%20disciplined%20lifestyle%20and%20healthy%20eating%20habits%20as%20essential%20complements%20to%20medical%20care.%20The%20full%20video%20of%20the%20press%20conference%20can%20be%20accessed%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20press%20conference%2C%20several%20media%20outlets%20pu