%3EJan%20Suraaj%20leader%20Prashant%20Kishor%20has%20said%20Bihar%20is%20%26quot%3Bliterally%20a%20failed%20state%26quot%3B%20which%20is%20in%20%26quot%3Bdeep%20s***%26quot%3B%20and%20tremendous%20efforts%20are%20required%20for%20its%20all-round%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20virtual%20interaction%20with%20the%20Bihari%20diaspora%20community%20after%20the%20launch%20of%20the%20US%20chapter%20of%20the%20Jan%20Suraaj%2C%20the%20former%20poll%20strategist%20exuded%20confidence%20that%20his%20party%20would%20win%20the%202025%20Bihar%20Assembly%20polls%20and%20said%20that%20he%20would%20lift%20the%20ban%20on%20alcohol%20and%20use%20the%20revenue%20to%20improve%20school%20education.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20to%20realise%20that%20this%20(Bihar)%20is%20a%20state%20which%20is%20in%20deep%20s***.%20If%20Bihar%20were%20a%20country%2C%20it%20would%20be%20the%2011th%20largest%20country%20in%20terms%20of%20population%20in%20the%20world.%20We%20have%20just%20overtaken%20Japan%20in%20terms%20of%20population%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kishor%20told%20the%20gathering.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20biggest%20challenge%20is%20that%20society%20has%20become%20%26quot%3Bhopeless%26quot%3B%20about%20improving%20the%20situation%20of%20Bihar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20become%20hopeless%2C%20the%20immediate%20survival%20needs%20become%20so%20overpowering%20that%20nothing%20(else)%20matters%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Mr%20Kishor%20said%2C%20not%20all%20is%20lost.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20hope%20is%20definitely%20there%20because%20of%20what%20we%20have%20been%20doing%20in%20the%20last%20two%20and%20a%20half%20years.%20But%20to%20convert%20this%20into%20a%20tangible%20electoral%20outcome%20and%20further%20into%20a%20governance%20outcome%20(will%20take%20time).%20Anyone%20who%20wants%20to%20be%20part%20of%20it%20has%20to%20be%20committed%20for%20at%20least%20five-six%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20if%20the%20government%20(of%20the%20Jan%20Suraaj)%20is%20formed%20in%202025%20and%20we%20continue%20to%20work%20hard%20with%20this%20intensity%2C%20it%20would%20be%20a%20big%20thing%20if%20Bihar%20becomes%20a%20middle-income%20state%20by%202029-2030.%20It%20is%20literally%20a%20failed%20state%20as%20it%20stands%20today%20on%20all%20developmental%20parameters%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kishor%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20characteristics%20of%20failed%20states%20are%20visible%20in%20the%20population%20here.%20For%20example...%20sometimes%20we%20think...%20why%20are%20people%20in%20Sudan%20fighting%20for%2020%20years%20in%20the%20civil%20war.%20Because%20when%20you%20are%20in%20that%20failed%20state%2C%20then%20people%20are%20not%20worried%20about%20how%20our%20children%20will%20study%20in%20Sudan.%20They%20are%20worried%20about%20who%20to%20shoot%20and%20where%20to%20capture.%20So%20that%20is%20the%20situation%20in%20Bihar%20too.%20And%20we%20must%20be%20aware%20of%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kishor%20told%20the%20Bihari%20diaspora%20community%20that%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Bnot%20trying%20to%20scare%20them%26quot%3B%20but%20making%20them%20aware%20of%20the%20ground%20realities%20and%20the%20long%20road%20ahead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Jan%20Suraaj%20will%20win%20in%202025%20(Bihar%20Assembly%20elections).%20There%20is%20no%20doubt%20about%20it.%20(Based%20on%20my)%20electoral%20understanding%2C%20I%20can%20clearly%20see%20that%20we%20will%20win%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20if%20the%20Jan%20Suraaj%20is%20voted%20to%20power%2C%20his%20top%20priority%20would%20be%20improving%20school%20education%20and%20this%20would%20be%20funded%20by%20the%20revenue%20generated%20after%20lifting%20the%20statewide%20ban%20on%20alcohol.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20urged%20members%20of%20the%20Bihari%20diaspora%20in%20the%20US%20to%20start%20calling%20their%20friends%20and%20relatives%20to%20support%20and%20vote%20for%20the%20Jan%20Suraaj.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Jan%20Suraaj%2C%20which%20was%20floated%20in%20October%20with%20much%20fanfare%2C%20failed%20to%20make%20an%20impact%20in%20the%20recent%20Bihar%20Assembly%20bypolls.%20The%20party's%20candidates%20lost%20deposits%20in%20all%20but%20one%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ruling%20NDA%20swept%20the%20bypolls%2C%20winning%20all%20four%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kishor%20further%20said%20the%20Bihari%20diaspora%20has%20not%20done%20much%20for%20the%20development%20of%20Bihar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20not%20seen%20anything%20very%20tangible%20on%20the%20ground.%20Beyond%20sessions%2C%20I%20have%20not%20seen%20anything%20tangible%20on%20the%20ground.%20Let%20me%20be%20blunt%20about%20it.%20Ultimately%2C%20you%20don't%20do%20anything.%20Don't%20take%20it%20otherwise.%20But%20you%20don't%20do%20anything%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20the%20gathering.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732541160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2F54bj05eo_prashant-kishor-_625x300_15_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fprashant-kishor-tells-bihari-community-in-us-bihar-is-literally-a-failed-state-7098513%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Jan%20Suraaj%20leader%20Prashant%20Kishor%20has%20said%20Bihar%20is%20%26quot%3Bliterally%20a%20failed%20state%26quot%3B%20which%20is%20in%20%26quot%3Bdeep%20s***%26quot%3B%20and%20tremendous%20efforts%20are%20required%20for%20its%20all-round%20development.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fprashant-kishor-tells-bihari-community-in-us-bihar-is-literally-a-failed-state-7098513%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22