0politics%20of%20performance%20has%20won%20in%20DU.%20Those%20who%20fought%20the%20election%20on%20false%20promises%20have%20lost.%20As%20a%20law%20student%2C%20I%20want%20to%20assure%20all%20the%20students%20in%20DU%20that%20we%20will%20stand%20with%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Khatri%20said%20after%20his%20election%20win.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20primary%20focus%20is%20to%20develop%20infrastructure.%20The%20changes%20that%20you%20have%20seen%20in%20law%20faculty%2C%20the%20same%20things%20will%20be%20implemented%20across%20the%20university%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EABVP's%20Mitravinda%20Karanwal%20has%20won%20the%20election%20for%20DUSU%20secretary's%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20first%20time%20after%202017%20that%20NSUI%20bagged%20two%20of%20the%20central%20posts%20and%20saw%20victory%20in%20the%20president's%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20total%2C%2021%20candidates%20were%20in%20the%20fray%20for%20four%20central%20posts.%20Out%20of%20these%2C%20eight%20contested%20the%20post%20of%20president%2C%20five%20vice-president%2C%20and%20four%20each%20fought%20the%20contest%20to%20become%20secretary%20and%20joint%20secretary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NSUI%20held%20the%20vice-president's%20post%20in%20the%20outgoing%20union%20while%20the%20ABVP%20held%20the%20remaining%20posts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20college-level%20elections%2C%20ABVP%20has%20achieved%20a%20clean%20sweep%20in%20five%20colleges%2C%20while%20NSUI%20won%20all%20positions%20in%20two%20colleges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20key%20players%20in%20the%20elections%20were%20ABVP%2C%20NSUI%2C%20and%20the%20Left-alliance%20of%20the%20All%20India%20Students'%20Association%20(AISA)%20and%20Students'%20Federation%20of%20India%20(SFI).%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732538280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fktrcsnio_dusu-polls_625x300_25_November_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fdusu-election-re