p%3E%26quot%3BIn%20my%20discussion%20with%20Fadnavis%2C%20I%20was%20informed%20that%20the%20Cabinet%20formation%20will%20be%20decided%20shortly%2C%20and%20the%20oath-taking%20ceremony%20will%20take%20place%20in%20the%20next%20two%20to%20three%20days.%20I%20have%20been%20assured%20that%20the%20RPI-A%20will%20also%20be%20allocated%20a%20ministry%20in%20the%20Cabinet%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Athawale%20told%20IANS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20Minister%20expressed%20confidence%20in%20Mr%20Fadnavis'%20leadership%2C%20asserting%2C%20%26quot%3BDevendra%20Fadnavis%20will%20be%20chosen%20as%20the%20next%20Chief%20Minister.%20The%20BJP%20has%20got%20132%20seats.%20Ajit%20Pawar%20also%20extended%20the%20support%20of%2041%20seats%20to%20Devendra%20Fadnavis.%20Discussions%20with%20Eknath%20Shinde%20are%20still%20underway.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Athawale%20also%20suggested%20that%20Eknath%20Shinde%2C%20who%20led%20Shiv%20Sena%20to%20win%2058%20seats%2C%20should%20be%20honoured%20with%20a%20central%20position%2C%20while%20Shiv%20Sena%20should%20get%20one%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShinde's%20contribution%20is%20significant%2C%20with%2057%20seats%20and%20notable%20developmental%20work%20over%20the%20past%202.5%20years.%20We%20respect%20his%20efforts%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20recently-concluded%20Maharashtra%20Assembly%20elections%2C%20the%20BJP%20emerged%20as%20the%20single-largest%20party%2C%20securing%20132%20seats%2C%20followed%20by%20Shinde-led%20Shiv%20Sena%20with%2057%20and%20Ajit%20Pawar-led%20NCP%20with%2041.%20The%20Mahayuti%20alliance%20collectively%20won%20a%20record%20230%20of%20the%20288%20seats%2C%20marking%20a%20historic%20victory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20broke%20its%20previous%20records%20of%20105%20seats%20in%202019%20and%20122%20in%202014%2C%20strengthening%20its%20claim%20for%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20post.%20Mr%20Fadnavis%20remains%20the%20frontrunner%2C%20with%20broad