C%20did%20not%20have%20authority%20to%20seize%20them.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A104%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc245jrdpmjgo%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc245jrdpmjgo.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc245jrdpmjgo.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BWell-Positioned%20For%20Future%26quot%3B%3A%20Top%20Investment%20Firm%20GQG%20Backs%20Adani%20Group%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Adani%20Group%20is%20%26quot%3Bwell-positioned%20for%20the%20future%26quot%3B%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bfundamentals%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20companies%20remain%20sound%2C%20underscored%20top%20investment%20firm%20GQG%20Partners%2C%20backing%20the%20group%20amid%20the%20US%20federal%20indictment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20recognize%20the%20distinction%20of%20the%20allegations%20of%20the%20individuals%20vs%20the%20companies.%20We%20believe%20the%20fundamentals%20of%20the%20companies%20we%20are%20invested%20in%20remain%20sound.%20As%20we%20do%20with%20other%20holdings%2C%20our%20team%20continues%20to%20do%20research%20and%20reassess%20the%20situation%20but%20as%20of%20now%20we%20have%20not%20changed%20our%20view%20on%20the%20prospects%20for%20these%20investments%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20GQG%20Partners%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGQG%20Partners%20cited%20the%20example%20of%20multiple%20global%20companies%20-%20Walmart%2C%20Oracle%2C%20Siemens%2C%20Petrobras%2C%20Pfizer%2C%20Toyota%20-%20facing%20similar%20government%20action%2C%20adding%20that%20%26quot%3Bthese%20actions%20and%20investigation%20typically%20take%20years%20to%20resolve%20and%20may%20yield%20reduced%20penalties%20or%20fines%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20indictment%20is%20happening%20during%20a%20period%20of%20transition%20for%20the%20US%20federal%20government%2C%20which%20means%20the%20case%20will%20likely%20continue%20under%20a%20new%20Justice%20Department%2C%20appointed%20by%20the%20Trump%20administration.%20We%20feel%20the%20Indian%20government%20will%20maintain%20its%20support%20for%20Gautam%20Adani%20as%20he%20is%20the%20most%20important%20infrastructure%20developer%20in%20the%20country%20by%20order%20of%20magnitude%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20company%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENone%20of%20the%20Adani%20Group's%2011%20public%20companies%20is%20implicated%20or%20accused%20of%20any%20wrongdoing%2C%20the%20group's%20Chief%20Financial%20Officer%20(CFO)%20Jugeshinder%20Singh%20said%20last%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Adani%20Group%20has%20strongly%20condemned%20the%20US%20report%2C%20terming%20it%20%26quot%3Bbaseless.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20the%20facts%20currently%20stand%20on%2021%20November%2C%20we%20do%20not%20see%20these%20actions%20as%20having%20a%20material%20impact%20on%20these%20businesses%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20GQG%20Partners%2C%20one%20of%20the%20first%20investors%20to%20acquire%20a%20stake%20in%20the%20Adani%20Group%20following%20last%20year's%20Hindenburg%20row.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20September-end%2C%20GQG%20Partners%20held%20a%20stake%20in%20six%20Adani%20Group%20companies%2C%20which%20ranged%20between%201.5%25%20and%202%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20DOJ%20indictment%20and%20SEC%20action%20are%20against%20individuals%20only.%20The%20allegations%20relate%20only%20to%20AGEL%2C%20not%20other%20Adani%20companies.%20While%20the%20allegations%20are%20serious%2C%20there%20are%20many%20examples%20of%20global%20companies%20and%20their%20executives%20who%20have%20faced%20significant%20government%20action%2C%20including%20Foreign%20Corrupt%20Practices%20Act%20(FCPA)%20violations.%20Some%20notable%20examples%20include%20Wal-Mart%2C%20Oracle%2C%20Thales%2C%20Siemens%2C%20Glencore%2C%20Petrobras%2C%20Pfizer%2C%20Toyota%2C%20Honeywell%2C%20Airbus%2C%20and%20SAP%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20investment%20firm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20seen%20a%20domino%20effect%20across%20Adani%20Group%20companies%2C%20but%20declines%20were%20mixed.%20We%20believe%20that%20investors%20were%20able%20to%20differentiate%20between%20the%20facts%20related%20to%20the%20individuals%20and%20the%20respective%20companies%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20firm%20said%20responding%20to%20the%20impact%20on%20markets%20in%20view%20of%20the%20US%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20today%2C%20the%20Adani%20Group%20announced%20robust%20financial%20health%20and%20steady%20growth%20through%20its%20latest%20H1%20FY25%20and%20Trailing-Twelve-Month%20(TTM)%20results%2C%20despite%20external%20pressures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Trailing-Twelve-Month%20EBITDA%20%C2%A0-%20%C2%A0earnings%20before%20interest%2C%20taxes%2C%20depreciation%2C%20and%20amortisation%20-%20surged%2017%20per%20cent%20YoY%20to%20USD%2010%20billion.%20Simultaneously%2C%20funds%20from%20operations%20(FFO)%20reached%20USD%207%20billion%2C%20growing%20at%20over%2030%20per%20cent%20annually%20for%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Disclaimer%3A%20New%20Delhi%20Television%20is%20a%20subsidiary%20of%20AMG%20Media%20Networks%20Limited%2C%20an%20Adani%20Group%20Company.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732537080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Faai84kao_adani-group-logo-reuters_625x300_29_July_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcontinue-to-believe-in-all-adani-companies-well-positioned-for-future-top-investment-firm-gqg-backs-adani-group-7102362%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Adani%20Group%20is%20%26quot%3Bwell-positioned%20for%20the%20future%26quot%3B%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bfundamentals%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20companies%20remain%20sound%2C%20underscored%20top%20investment%20firm%20GQG%20Partners%2C%20backing%20the%20group%20amid%20the%20US%20federal%20indictment.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22