%2C%20Mid-Day%20Meal%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESchools%20in%20the%20National%20Capital%20Region%20should%20open%20now%20despite%20the%20high%20pollution%20levels%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20said%20today%2C%20pointing%20to%20three%20issues%20that%20will%20not%20get%20solved%20if%20students%20stay%20home.%C2%A0The%20court%2C%20though%2C%20left%20the%20final%20decision%20to%20the%20CAQM%20(Commission%20for%20Air%20Quality%20Management)%2C%20including%20the%20one%20on%20continuing%20the%20ban%20on%20physical%20classes%20for%20Classes%2010%20and%2012.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%C2%A0large%20number%20of%20students%20do%20not%20have%20air%20purifiers%20in%20their%20homes%20and%20hence%20there%20is%20no%20difference%20between%20children%20sitting%20at%20home%20and%20children%20going%20to%20school%2C%20the%20judges%20said.%20Moreover%2C%20a%20large%20number%20of%20students%20do%20not%20have%20the%20facilities%20to%20participate%20in%20online%20education%20and%20will%20fall%20behind%20if%20the%20online%20classes%20continue%20further.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20but%20not%20the%20least%2C%20the%20court%20said%2C%20a%20number%20of%20students%20are%20being%20deprived%20of%20the%20mid-day%20meal%20facility%20as%20schools%20and%20anganwadis%20remain%20closed%2C%20the%20judges%20pointed%20out.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLet%20the%20commission%20take%20a%20decision%20at%20the%20earliest%20even%20without%20copy%20of%20the%20order...%20we%20expect%20a%20decision%20to%20be%20taken%20latest%20by%20today%20or%20tomorrow%20morning%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20judges%20said%20in%20their%20order.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20order%20today%2C%20the%20top%20court%20also%20said%20that%20due%20to%20the%20implementation%20of%20GRAP%204%20rules%2C%20many%20sections%20of%20society%20have%20been%20adversely%20affected.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20section%20of%20society%20adversely%20affected%20due%20to%20GRAP%20IV%20(rules)%20and%20the%20commission%20(CAQM)%20has%20all%20the%20powers%20under%20the%20act%20to%20issue%20directions%20to%20various%20authorities%20to%20ensure%20that%20persons%20in%20category%20in%20labourers%20and%20daily%20wagers%20do%20not%20suffer.%20Thus%20we%20direct%20commission%20to%20take%20several%20mitigating%20measures%20under%20Section%2012%20of%20the%20Act%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20judges%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20chart%20on%20the%20Air%20Quality%20Index%20in%20the%20NCR%20region%20has%20been%20submitted%20and%20it%20shows%20AQI%20from%20Nov%2020%20to%2023%20ranges%20from%20300%20to%20419.%20We%20direct%20commission%20to%20place%20the%20updated%20data%20on%20next%20date%20so%20that%20court%20can%20take%20steps%20on%20Grade%204%20measures%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20top%20court%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732535940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2F4go3da7_delhi-pollution_625x300_20_November_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-schools-to-reopen-top-court-says-many-dont-have-air-purifier-mid-day-meal-7102100%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Schools%20in%20Delhi%20can%20open%20now%20despite%20the%20high%20pollution%20levels%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20said%20today%2C%20pointing%20to%20three%20issues%20that%20will%20not%20get%20solved%20if%20students%20stay%20home.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-schools-to-reopen-top-court-says-many-dont-have-air-purifier-mid-day-meal-7102100%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Who%20Is%20Allah%20Ghazanfar%3A%2018-Year-Old%20Spinner%20Who%20Went%20For%20Rs%204.8%20Crore%20To%20MI%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAfghanistan%20spinner%C2%A0Allah%20Ghazanfar%20hit%20the%20jackpot%20in%20the%20IPL%202025%20Auction%20as%20the%2018-year-old%20was%20bought%20by%20Mumbai%20Indians%20for%20Rs%204.8%20crore%20on%20Monday.%20The%20spinner%20has%20been%20enjoying%20a%20brilliant%20run%20of%20form%20in%20the%20recent%20past%20with%20his%20devastating%20spell%20in%20the%20ODI%20series%20against%20Bangladesh%20making%20headlines.%20KKR%20were%20interested%20in%20buying%20him%20back%20but%20at%20the%20end%20of%20an%20intense%20bidding%20war%2C%20it%20was%20Mumbai%20Indians%20who%20emerged%20victorious%20and%20they%20ended%20up%20adding%20the%20talented%20spinner%20to%20their%20ranks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGhazanfar%20started%20his%20cricketing%20journey%20as%20a%20fast%20bowler%20before%20former%20Afghanistan%20skipper%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Dawlat%20Ahmadzai%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1310-dawlat-ahmadzai-playerprofile%5C%22%3EDawlat%20Ahmadzai%3C%2Fa%3E%20turned%20him%20into%20a%20mystery%20spinner.%20He%20grabbed%20headlines%20with%20his%20brilliant%20showing%20during%20the%202024%20U-19%20World%20Cup%20where%20he%20finished%20with%20eight%20wickets%20in%20four%20matches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20was%20enough%20to%20earn%20him%20a%20senior%20team%20call-up%20as%20he%20made%20his%20ODI%20debut%20against%20Ireland.%20He%20continued%20to%20impress%20and%20even%20won%20the%20Player%20of%20the%20Match%20award%20in%20the%20Emerging%20Asia%20Cup%20final%20against%20Sri%20Lanka%20A%20as%20Afghanistan%20went%20on%20to%20clinch%20the%20title.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20young%20spinner%20was%20also%20part%20of%20the%20Kolkata%20Knight%20Riders%20(KKR)%20side%20that%20went%20on%20to%20win%20the%20IPL%202024%20title.%20He%20was%20added%20to%20the%20squad%20as%20a%20replacement%20for%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Mujeeb%20Ur%20Rahman%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F108606-mujeeb-zadran-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMujeeb%20Ur%20Rahman%3C%2Fa%3E%20but%20did%20not%20play%20any%20matches%20for%20the%20franchise%20in%20the%20campaign.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERoyal%20Challengers%20Bengaluru%20shelled%20out%20big%20bucks%20for%20seasoned%20pacer%20Bhuvneshwar%20Kumar%2C%20while%20Deepak%20Chahar%20made%20an%20'El%20Clasico'%20move%20from%20Chennai%20to%20Mumbai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20capped%20bowlers%20set%2C%20Tushar%20Deshpande%20fetched%20a%20big%20price%20for%20himself.%20His%20former%20side%2C%20CSK%2C%20came%20in%20quickly%20for%20him%20at%20Rs%201%20crore%2C%20and%20Rajasthan%20Royals%20jumped%20in%20at%20Rs%201.20%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20CSK%20and%20RR%20kept%20at%20it%2C%20with%20the%20former%20expressing%20their%20intention%20of%20bringing%20Deshpande%20back%20to%20Chepauk.%20RR%20was%20firm%20in%20its%20stance%20and%20moved%20the%20bid%20up%20to%20Rs%205%20crore%20and%20quickly%20up%20to%20Rs%206%20crore.%20CSK%20took%20a%20final%20gamble%20by%20raising%20the%20paddle%20for%20Rs%206.25%20crore.%20But%20RR%20pushed%20their%20bid%20to%20Rs%206.50%20crore%20and%20made%20Deshpande%20a%20Royal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGerald%20Coetzee%20was%20a%20quick%20steal%20by%20Gujarat%20Titans%20for%20Rs%202.4%20crore%20despite%20some%20interest%20from%20a%20couple%20of%20franchises.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBhuvneshwar%20Kumar%2C%20a%20two-time%20Purple%20Cap%20winner%20and%20a%20household%20name%20in%20the%20cash-rich%20league%2C%20appeared%20in%20the%20auction%20with%20a%20base%20price%20of%20Rs%202%20crore.%20Mumbai%20raised%20the%20paddle%20straightaway%20with%20LSG%20coming%20in%20swiftly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20proper%20bidding%20war%20for%20Bhuvneshwar%2C%20with%20franchises%20willing%20to%20break%20the%20bank%20for%20his%20services.%20LSG%20raised%20the%20bid%20to%20Rs%2010%20crore%2C%20which%20made%20MI%20back%20out.%20It%20seemed%20the%20deal%20was%20done%20and%20dusted%2C%20but%20RCB%20came%20right%20at%20the%20end%20to%20acquire%20the%20seasoned%20quick%20for%20a%20price%20tag%20of%20Rs%2010.75%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(With%20ANI%20inputs)%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732534860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fd6sfsa9o_allah-ghazanfar_625x300_25_November_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2025%2Fwho-is-allah-ghazanfar-18-year-old-spinner-who-went-for-rs-4-8-crore-to-mumbai-indians-in-ipl-2025-auction-7102228%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Afghanistan%20spinner%20Allah%20Ghazanfar%20hit%20the%20jackpot%20in%20the%20IPL%202025%20Auction%20as%20the%2018-year-old%20was%20bought%20by%20Mumbai%20Indians%20for%20Rs%204.8%20crore.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A91%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2025%2Fwho-is-allah-ghazanfar-18-year-old-spinner-who-went-for-rs-4-8-crore-to-mumbai-indians-in-ipl-2025-auction-7102228%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BLeft%20India%20Because%20Of%20Death%20Threats%20From%20Dawood%20Ibrahim%26quot%3B%3A%20Lalit%20Modi%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ELalit%20Modi%2C%20founder%20of%20the%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL)%2C%20revealed%20that%20he%20left%20India%20in%202010%2C%20not%20because%20of%20legal%20troubles%2C%20but%20because%20of%20life-threatening%20pressure%20from%20underworld%20don%20Dawood%20Ibrahim.%20Mr%20Modi%20made%20the%20claim%20in%20a%20recent%20episode%20of%20Raj%20Shamani's%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2Cnoindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DBELiyff0K7Y%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epodcast%3C%2Fa%3E%20'Figuring%20Out'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20left%20the%20country%20when%20I%20got%20death%20threats%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Modi%20said%20in%20the%20interview.%20%26quot%3BInitially%2C%20there%20was%20no%20legal%20issue%20that%20forced%20me%20to%20leave%20the%20country.%20I%20got%20death%20threats%20from%20Dawood%20Ibrahim.%20Dawood%20Ibrahim%20was%20after%20me%20because%20he%20wanted%20to%20fix%20matches.%20I%20had%20a%20'zero%20policy'%20on%20fixing%20matches.%20For%20me%2C%20the%20anti-corruption%20campaign%20was%20very%20important%20and%20I%20felt%20the%20integrity%20of%20the%20game%20was%20very%20important.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Modi%20claimed%20that%20his%20personal%20bodyguard%20urged%20him%20to%20use%20the%20VIP%20exit%20at%20the%20airport%20for%20safety.%20Things%20escalated%20when%20senior%20police%20officials%20informed%20him%20that%20he%20was%20on%20a%20hitlist%20and%20could%20be%20guaranteed%20protection%20for%20only%2012%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHimanshu%20Roy%2C%20the%20Deputy%20Commissioner%20of%20Police%2C%20was%20waiting%20for%20me%20at%20the%20airport%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Modi%20said.%20%26quot%3BHe%20told%20me%2C%20'We%20cannot%20protect%20you%20anymore.%20There%20is%20a%20hit%20on%20your%20life.%20We%20can%20only%20ensure%20your%20safety%20for%20the%20next%2012%20hours.'%20From%20there%2C%20I%20was%20escorted%20to%20the%20Four%20Seasons%20Hotel%20in%20Mumbai.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Modi%20added%20in%20the%20interview%20that%20he%20can%20return%20to%20India%20%26quot%3Bany%20day%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20can%20return%20tomorrow%20morning%20to%20India%2C%20but%20my%20issue%20is%20not%20to%20go.%20Legally%20I%20am%20not%20a%20fugitive.%20There%20is%20not%20a%20single%20case%20in%20any%20court.%20If%20there%20is%2C%20then%20please%20produce%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Modi%20being%20on%20D-Company's%20hit%20list%20is%20well%20known.%20A%20few%20years%20ago%2C%20Chhota%20Shakeel%2C%20Dawood's%20trusted%20lieutenant%2C%20revealed%20in%20an%20interview%20that%20a%20team%20of%20sharpshooters%2C%20following%20the%20underworld%20don's%20instructions%2C%20landed%20in%20Thailand's%20capital%20Bangkok%20where%20Mr%20Modi%20was%20staying.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChhota%20Shakeel%20claimed%20that%20he%20and%20his%20team%20of%20shooters%20arrived%20at%20the%20hotel%20where%20Mr%20Modi%20was%20to%20kill%20him%20but%20the%20former%20IPL%20chairman%20managed%20to%20escape%2C%20thanks%20to%20someone%20tipping%20him%20off.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732534740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22h