%9CThe%20goal%20is%20to%20make%20menstrual%20health%20education%20a%20universal%20right%20and%20to%20get%20rid%20of%20the%20barriers%20that%20prevent%20underprivileged%20children%20and%20women%20from%20getting%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F369350%2Fdr-abhay-bang-rani-search-gadchiroli-maharashtra-tribal-healthcare-access%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eproper%20education%20and%20healthcare%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Preeti.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20achieve%20that%20goal%2C%20Prazna%20launched%20Project%20Kishori%2C%20which%20aims%20to%20educate%20young%20girls%20about%20menstrual%20hygiene%20and%20provide%20them%20with%20essential%20hygiene%20kits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-20-at-4.29.19-PM_11zon-1732170305.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Preeti%20speaking%20to%20a%20group%20of%20girls%20at%20a%20government%20school%20in%20Jaipur%2C%20educating%20them%20about%20menstrual%20health%2C%20the%20importance%20of%20hygiene%2C%20and%20empowering%20them%20to%20speak%20openly%20about%20periods%20without%20shame.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-20-at-4.29.19-PM_11zon-1732170305.jpeg%201280w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-20-at-4.29.19-PM_11zon-1732170305-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-20-at-4.29.19-PM_11zon-1732170305-500x375.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-20-at-4.29.19-PM_11zon-1732170305-768x576.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-20-at-4.29.19-PM_11zon-1732170305-1200x900.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-20-at-4.29.19-PM_11zon-1732170305-800x600.jpeg%20800w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-20-at-4.29.19-PM_11zon-1732170305-600x450.jpeg%20600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-20-at-4.29.19-PM_11zon-1732170305-400x300.jpeg%20400w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-20-at-4.29.19-PM_11zon-1732170305-200x150.jpeg%20200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-20-at-4.29.19-PM_11zon-1732170305-150x113.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-381669%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EPrazna%20has%20set%20up%20Project%20Kishori%20in%20over%20100%20schools%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20Project%20Kishori%20is%20the%20cornerstone%20of%20Prazna%E2%80%99s%20efforts%20in%20creating%20menstrual%20health%20awareness%20among%20schoolchildren%2C%20especially%20in%20marginalised%20communities.%20%E2%80%9CSanitary%20pads%20are%20affordable%20now%2C%20the%20Government%20also%20hands%20them%20out.%20But%20we%20have%20worked%20with%20women%20who%20come%20from%20the%20labour%20class%20and%20don%E2%80%99t%20even%20have%20the%20money%20to%20buy%20underwear%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Preeti.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20help%20women%20prioritise%20hygiene%20during%20menstruation%2C%20the%20foundation%20gives%20women%20a%20comprehensive%20kit%20of%20essentials%20that%20includes%20underwear%2C%20garbage%20bags%20(to%20teach%20proper%20disposal)%2C%20antiseptic%20liquids%20for%20hygienic%20wash%2C%20and%20paper%20soaps%20to%20encourage%20proper%20handwashing%20habits.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeyond%20the%20kits%2C%20Project%20Kishori%20largely%20focuses%20on%20educating%20girls%20about%20their%20bodies%2C%20helping%20them%20understand%20the%20menstrual%20cycle%2C%20and%20creating%20a%20safe%20space%20for%20them%20to%20ask%20questions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%E2%80%99ve%20covered%20over%20100%20schools%20within%20two%20months%2C%20both%20in%20and%20around%20Jaipur.%20And%20these%20are%20remote%20areas%20where%20nobody%20ever%20goes%2C%E2%80%9D%20Preeti%20mentions.%20Through%20this%20outreach%2C%20Prazna%20has%20already%20educated%20over%2020%2C000%20women%20on%20menstruation%20and%20hygiene.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%E2%80%99s%20unique%20about%20Project%20Kishori%20is%20its%20approach%20to%20breaking%20down%20the%20taboos%20around%20menstruation%20through%20peer-to-peer%20interaction.%20In%20each%20school%2C%20%E2%80%98Kishori%20Clubs%E2%80%99%20were%20established%2C%20bringing%20together%20girls%20who%20would%20lead%20conversations%20and%20share%20their%20experiences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20seen%20a%20lot%20of%20girls%2C%20especially%20if%20they%20get%20their%20periods%20young%2C%20get%20very%20nervous.%20They%20have%20no%20idea%20how%20to%20deal%20with%20it.%20What%20Prazna%20and%20Preeti%20do%20is%20give%20a%20certain%20sense%20of%20reassurance%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%C2%A0%20Kavita%20Sharma%2C%20principal%20of%20a%20government%20school%20in%20Jaipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20also%20help%20girls%20navigate%20this%20next%20stage%20of%20their%20life%2C%20whether%20it%20be%20emotionally%2C%20mentally%20or%20physically%2C%20because%20it%20is%20a%20lot%20for%20one%20small%20person%20to%20go%20through%20on%20their%20own%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBuilding%20trust%20and%20understanding%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20creating%20an%20environment%20where%20girls%20feel%20comfortable%2C%20the%20programme%20encourages%20ongoing%20conversations%20about%20menstrual%20health.%20One%20strategy%20employed%20by%20Prazna%20was%20to%20use%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F278313%2Fsundarbans-hingalganj-island-english-medium-school-inspiring-teacher-kolkata%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efemale%20teachers%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20intermediaries%20%E2%80%94%20trusted%20adults%20who%20could%20help%20facilitate%20conversations%20between%20the%20girls%20and%20the%20organisation.%20This%20method%20not%20only%20helped%20ensure%20privacy%20and%20trust%20but%20also%20empowered%20local%20educators%20to%20take%20ownership%20of%20the%20initiative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201100px)%20100vw%2C%201100px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-20-at-4.29.12-PM-1732170448.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221100%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Diya%20Kumari%2C%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20Rajasthan%2C%20addressing%20issues%20of%20period%20shame%20and%20stigma%2C%20while%20supporting%20menstrual%20health%20education%20and%20empowerment.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-20-at-4.29.12-PM-1732170448.jpeg%201100w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-20-at-4.29.12-PM-1732170448-300x200.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-20-at-4.29.12-PM-1732170448-500x334.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-m