2C%20bowl%2C%20and%20collar.%20The%20bed%20was%20intended%20to%20measure%20weight%20and%20sync%20the%20data%20to%20the%20cloud%2C%20the%20bowl%20to%20monitor%20food%20and%20water%20intake%2C%20and%20the%20collar%20to%20track%20vital%20signs%2C%E2%80%9D%20recalls%20Vani.%20%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20when%20we%20presented%20the%20concept%20to%20veterinarians%2C%20they%20urged%20us%20to%20create%20a%20device%20capable%20of%20providing%20precise%20measurements%20and%20actionable%20data%20for%20accurate%20diagnosis%20and%20prognosis.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Vivek%20and%20Vani%20started%20the%20business%2C%20the%20first%20agency%20they%20hired%20was%20a%20Chennai-based%20law%20firm%20%E2%80%98KRIA%20Law%E2%80%99%20as%20they%20had%20patents%20to%20file%20on%20their%20inventions.%20They%20were%20recommended%20to%20the%20IIT%20Madras%20Incubation%20Cell%20by%20the%20founder%20of%20KRIA%20Law%2C%20M%20S%20Bharath.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20we%20worked%20on%20the%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F263411%2Frashi-narang-heads-up-for-tails-delhi-pet-startup-earns-crores%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20bed%2C%20bowl%2C%20and%20collar%3C%2Fa%3E%20platform%20and%20began%20developing%20our%20proprietary%20device%2C%20we%20sought%20the%20expertise%20of%20KRIA%20Law%2C%20a%20legal%20agency%20that%20guided%20us%20in%20filing%20patents%20and%20a%20PCT%20(Patent%20Cooperation%20Treaty)%20for%20our%20IoT%20devices%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Vani.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20journey%20took%20a%20significant%20turn%20when%20Bharath%20introduced%20them%20to%20Professor%20Ashok%20Jhunjhunwala%2C%20who%20was%20thrilled%20by%20their%20innovative%20efforts.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Incubation%20Cell%20has%20been%20instrumental%20in%20our%20growth%2C%20offering%20everything%20from%20office%20spaces%20to%20insightful%20mentoring%20sessions%20and%20valuable%20industry%20connections%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%20%E2%80%9CThey%E2%80%99ve%20supported%20us%20through%20funding%20discussions%2C%20pitch%20deck%20management%2C%20and%20more.%20They%20continue%20to%20be%20the%20wind%20beneath%20our%20wings.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAssisting%20Vivek%20and%20Vani%20are%20chief%20technology%20officer%20Karthikeyan%20Gururaj%2C%20who%20also%20lost%20two%20of%20his%20pets%20to%20medical%20emergencies.%20For%20Karthikeyan%2C%20the%20startup%20was%20initially%20a%20client%20for%20technology%20platform%20development%20but%20he%20soon%20realised%20that%20the%20devices%20they%20were%20developing%20could%20have%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F268184%2Fdelhi-kitchen-for-paws-feed-stray-dogs-animals-food-divya-gurwara%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaved%20his%20dogs%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20decided%20to%20join%20their%20mission.%20The%20fourth%20key%20person%20to%20join%20them%20was%20S%20Rajkumar%2C%20who%20is%20pursuing%20his%20master%E2%80%99s%20in%20biomedical%20design%20at%20IIT%20Madras.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EExam%20D%3A%20A%20non-invasive%20solution%20for%20accurate%20diagnoses%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20Vani%20and%20Vivek%20have%20three%20pet%20dogs%20each.%20As%20Vani%20argues%2C%20a%20major%20challenge%20in%20dealing%20with%20pet%20dogs%20is%20their%20high%20tolerance%20for%20pain%2C%20which%20makes%20it%20difficult%20for%20pet%20owners%20like%20her%20to%20recognise%20any%20real%20signs%20of%20discomfort.%20With%20a%20human%20child%2C%20you%20check%20their%20forehead%20to%20see%20if%20they%20have%20a%20fever%20and%20give%20them%20some%20soup.%20With%20dogs%2C%20however%2C%20you%20can%E2%80%99t%20touch%20their%20forehead%20and%20gauge%20whether%20they%20have%20a%20fever%20