0in%20an%20executive%20summary%20will%20be%20available%20as%20a%20user%20goes%20through%20the%20prompts%20of%20the%20app%20and%20device%E2%80%99s%20graphic%20user%20interface%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Vani.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProfessor%20K%20Rajkumar%2C%20head%20of%20the%20Veterinary%20Clinical%20Complex%20at%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20College%20of%20Veterinary%20and%20Animal%20Sciences%2C%20Pondicherry%2C%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20device%20is%20very%20convenient%2C%20especially%20for%20pet%20owners.%20They%20can%20easily%20use%20it%20to%20measure%20their%20pet%E2%80%99s%20temperature%2C%20heart%20rate%2C%20and%20lung%20(respiratory)%20sounds%20by%20simply%20placing%20it%20near%20the%20animal.%20The%20recorded%20data%20can%20then%20be%20shared%20with%20a%20veterinarian%20through%20telemedicine%20for%20further%20analysis.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSnapinsta.app_394118659_731097555730933_1985252946786160050_n_1080-1732274787-500x625.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Exam%20D%20device%20developed%20by%20Vetinstant%20for%20Pet%20Parents%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSnapinsta.app_394118659_731097555730933_1985252946786160050_n_1080-1732274787-500x625.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSnapinsta.app_394118659_731097555730933_1985252946786160050_n_1080-1732274787-240x300.jpg%20240w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSnapinsta.app_394118659_731097555730933_1985252946786160050_n_1080-1732274787-150x188.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSnapinsta.app_394118659_731097555730933_1985252946786160050_n_1080-1732274787.jpg%20767w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-382095%5C%22