0helped%20us%20when%20my%20father%20was%20battling%20a%20prolonged%20illness%20and%20during%20the%20final%20days%20of%20my%20elder%20brother%2C%20who%20was%20mentally%20challenged.%20Every%20time%20I%20called%20her%20during%20tough%20times%2C%20despite%20the%20hour%2C%20she%20always%20made%20sure%20that%20we%20had%20clarity%20and%20felt%20at%20peace%20after%20the%20conversation.%E2%80%9D%20Ketan%20is%20grateful%20for%20what%20Alpa%20has%20done%20and%20continues%20to%20stay%20in%20touch%20with%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EMany%20patients%20ask%20%E2%80%9CWhy%20me%3F%E2%80%9D%20after%20their%20diagnosis.%20Alpa%20encourages%20them%20to%20instead%20say%2C%20%E2%80%9CTry%20me!%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDrawing%20from%20her%20own%20experiences%2C%20Alpa%20also%20believes%20emotions%20can%20correlate%20with%20certain%20illnesses.%20%E2%80%9CFor%20instance%2C%20I%E2%80%99ve%20observed%20many%20breast%20cancer%20patients%20have%20unresolved%20%E2%80%98mothering%E2%80%99%20issues%20%E2%80%94%20either%20with%20their%20mothers%20or%20their%20children.%20While%20I%20respect%20medical%20science%2C%20my%20work%20has%20broadened%20my%20perspective%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20reflects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EEncouraging%20empathy%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFluent%20in%20seven%20languages%20%E2%80%94%20Hindi%2C%20Kannada%2C%20Tamil%2C%20to%20name%20a%20few%20%E2%80%94%20and%20sign%20language%2C%20Alpa%20ensures%20her%20counselling%20is%20accessible%20to%20a%20diverse%20group%20of%20patients.%20%E2%80%9CI%20once%20worked%20with%20a%20deaf%20and%20mute%20woman%20who%20was%20worried%20about%20losing%20her%20long%20hair%20to%20chemotherapy.%20Using%20simple%20actions%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20address%20her%20concerns.%20Unfortunately%2C%20many%20government%20hospitals%20lack%20resources%20for%20such%2