n%2C%20along%20with%20stone%2C%20wood%2C%20and%20slate.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cottages%20are%20an%20aesthetic%20rebuttal%20to%20the%20assumption%20that%20sustainability%20comes%20at%20the%20price%20of%20beauty.%20We%20virtually%20go%20from%20room%20to%20room%2C%20that%20are%20a%20carousel%20of%20local%20architectural%20sensibilities%2C%20right%20from%20their%20roofs%20%E2%80%94%20inspired%20by%20the%20%3Cem%3Egaddi%20%3C%2Fem%3Etribe%20homes%20which%20imbibe%20ingenious%20leakage%20management%20concepts%20%E2%80%94%20to%20the%20decor.%20Hand-chiselled%20river%20stones%20factor%20into%20the%20construction%2C%20and%20the%20no-paint%20mandate%20is%20taken%20seriously.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20is%20the%20woodwork%20that%20has%20the%20best%20story%20to%20tell.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUpasana%20articulates%20it.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20an%20old%20Palampur%20courthouse%20that%20was%20being%20demolished%20during%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F362584%2Fmedini-homestay-kaziranga-national-park-assam-sustainable-champak-deka-anna-louise-meynell%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econstruction%20of%20the%20cottages%3C%2Fa%3E.%20We%20were%20able%20to%20pick%20up%20and%20recycle%20the%20cedar%20and%20pine%20wood.%20The%20roof%20lining%20details%2C%20bannisters%20from%20witness%20stands%2C%20and%20even%20whole%20doors%20and%20windows%20are%20originally%20from%20the%20old%20courthouse.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20six%20years%20for%20the%20dream%20project%20to%20see%20the%20light%20of%20day.%20But%20when%20it%20did%2C%20Palampur%20smiled.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20cup%20of%20%3Cem%3Echai%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewith%20