d%20hands-on%20in%20building%20the%20prototype%20and%20consulted%20with%20professionals%2C%20electricians%2C%20and%20mechanics%20to%20bring%20my%20vision%20to%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20The%20process%20was%20incredibly%20time-consuming%2C%20with%20Suhani%20dedicating%20her%20mornings%20to%20planning%20her%20work%20and%20her%20evenings%20to%20check%20in%20with%20herself%20to%20see%20how%20much%20progress%20she%20had%20made.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuhani%E2%80%99s%20school%2C%20Amity%20International%2C%20Pushp%20Vihar%2C%20and%20her%20parents%20were%20instrumental%20in%20supporting%20her%20endeavours.%20Amity%20University%2C%20Noida%2C%20provided%20crucial%20guidance%2C%20helping%20her%20refine%20the%20project%20and%20conduct%20field%20research%20with%20farmers%2C%20which%20significantly%20improved%20the%20vehicle%E2%80%99s%20design.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EEnhancing%20design%20and%20performance%20of%20So-Apt%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20feedback%20I%20received%20from%20farmers%20was%20invaluable%2C%E2%80%9D%20Suhani%20shares.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20helped%20me%20understand%20the%20real%20challenges%20they%20face%20and%20guided%20me%20in%20making%20adjustments.%20For%20example%2C%20one%20of%20the%20main%20feedback%20was%20to%20increase%20the%20vertical%20spherence%20of%20the%20vehicle%2C%20which%20I%E2%80%99m%20currently%20working%20on%20improving.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFarmers%20also%20suggested%20improving%20the%20tires%2C%20which%20I%E2%80%99m%20refining%20for%20production.%20I%E2%80%99m%20also%20working%20on%20making%20the%20So-Apt%20vehicle%20smarter.%20As%20I%20enhance%20the%20vehicle%E2%80%99s%20energy%20capacity%20and%20add%20more%20tools%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20carefully%20balancing%20performance%20and%20cost%20to%20ensure%20it%20remains%20an%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D