-School-Pushp-Vihar-develops-a-path-breaking-innovation-SO-APT-1-1732018477-500x281.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSuhani-Chauhan-a-student-of-Amity-International-School-Pushp-Vihar-develops-a-path-breaking-innovation-SO-APT-1-1732018477-768x432.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSuhani-Chauhan-a-student-of-Amity-International-School-Pushp-Vihar-develops-a-path-breaking-innovation-SO-APT-1-1732018477-1536x864.jpeg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSuhani-Chauhan-a-student-of-Amity-International-School-Pushp-Vihar-develops-a-path-breaking-innovation-SO-APT-1-1732018477-1200x675.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSuhani-Chauhan-a-student-of-Amity-International-School-Pushp-Vihar-develops-a-path-breaking-innovation-SO-APT-1-1732018477-150x84.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-381149%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22899%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20So-Apt%20Agro%20vehicle%20has%20a%20range%20of%20features%20to%20make%20farming%20easy%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20standout%20aspects%20of%20the%20So-Apt%20vehicle%20is%20its%20solar-powered%20design.%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99ve%20always%20been%20inclined%20towards%20sustainability%2C%20and%20I%20wanted%20to%20create%20something%20that%20was%20environmentally%20friendly%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Suhani.%20The%20vehicle%20operates%20entirely%20on%20solar%20power%2C%20which%20reduces%20the%20reliance%20on%20expensive%20diesel%20and%20petrol%2C%20a%20major%20cost%20burden%20for%20farmers.%20In%20addition%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F352016%2Fhow-to-harvest-solar-energy-panels-in-apartments-homes-rentals-guide-to-save-electricity-bills%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esolar%20panels%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20vehicle%20provide%20an%20energy%20reserve%20that%20can%20be%20used%20for%20other%20purposes%2C%20further%20enhancing%20its%20value.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Suhani%20didn%E2%80%99t%20stop%20there.%20She%20included%20a%20backup%20engine%20that%20can%20be%20used%20during%20the%20rainy%20season%20or%20at%20night%2C%20ensuring%20that%20the%20vehicle%20remains%20functional%20even%20during%20unfavourable%20conditions.%20This%20combination%20of%20solar%20power%20and%20backup%20energy%20makes%20the%20So-Apt%20vehicle%20a%20truly%20sustainable%20solution%20for%20farmers%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20So-Apt%20is%20set%20to%20transform%20agriculture%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuhani%E2%80%99s%20commitment%20to%20sustainability%20is%20evident%20in%20her%20design.%20%E2%80%9CIndia%20is%20a%20country%20rich%20in%20solar%20energy%2C%20and%20I%20believe%20that%20harnessing%20this%20resource%20will%20be%20extremely%20beneficial%20for%20farmers%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20The%20vehicle%E2%80%99s%20solar%20panels%20are%20designed%20to%20last%20for%20several%20years%2C%20and%20Suhani%20is%20working%20on%20increasing%20the%20energy%20reserve%20to%20make%20the%20vehicle%20even%20more%20efficient.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20development%20of%20So-Apt%20has%20been%20a%20journey%20of%20constant%20iteration%2C%20fueled%20by%20feedback%20from%20the%20farming%20community.%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99ve%20spoken%20to%20over%201%2C000%20farmers%2C%20shown%20them%20the%20So-Apt%20vehicle%2C%20and%20listened%20to%20their%20feedback.%20Through%20countless%20conversations%20and%20research%2C%20I%E2%80%99ve%20gained%20a%20deeper%20understanding%20of%20their%20challenges%20and%20how%20my%20vehicle%20can%20make%20a%20difference.%20The%20joy%20and%20appreciation%20I%20see%20on%20their%20faces%2C%20knowing%20that%20young%20people%20like%20me%20are%20working%20to%20help%20them%2C%20keeps%20me%20motivated%20every%20day%2C%E2%80%9D%20Suhani%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20her%20future%20plans%20for%20So-Apt%2C%20Suhani%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99m%20working%20on%20adding%20a%20GPS%20system%20to%20help%20farmers%20track%20which%20parts%20of%20their%20field%20they%20have%20covered%20whether%20it%E2%80%99s%20for%20planting%2C%20irrigating%2C%20or%20applying%20fertilisers.%20This%20will%20make%20the%20farming%20process%20more%20efficient.%E2%80%9D%20She%E2%80%99s%20also%20incorporating%20a%20pH%20calculator%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F374594%2Fwinter-soil-health-india-tips-farmers-temperature-crops-compaction-microbial-activity%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emonitor%20soil%20healt%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F374594%2Fwinter-soil-health-india-tips-farmers-temperature-crops-compaction-microbial-activity%2F%5C%22%3Eh%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20further%20enhancing%20the%20vehicle%E2%80%99s%20functionality%20and%20making%20it%20an%20even%20more%20valuable%20tool%20for%20farmers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuhani%20is%20also%20focusing%20on%20making%20the%20vehicle%20smarter%20and%20easier%20to%20use%20for%20farmers.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20goal%20is%20to%20create%20a%20vehicle%20that%E2%80%99s%20not%20only%20affordable%20but%20also%20user-friendly.%20Farmers%20should%20be%20able%20to%20operate%20it%20without%20needing%20technical%20expertise%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20This%20focus%20on%20simplicity%20and%20functionality%20is%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20So-Apt%20vehicle%E2%80%99s%20design.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWinning%20the%20Rashtriya%20Bal%20Puraskar%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuhani%E2%80%99s%20unwavering%20dedication%20and%20tireless%20effort%20have%20certainly%20not%20escaped%20attention.%20In%20January%202024%2C%20she%20was%20honoured%20with%20the%20Pradhan%20Mantri%20Rashtriya%20Bal%20Puraskar%20Award.%20%E2%80%9CI%20remember%20my%20mother%20calling%20me%20and%20telling%20me%20I%20won%20the%20award.%20Words%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20describe%20what%20I%20was%20feeling%20at%20that%20moment%2C%E2%80%9D%20Suhani%20recalls.%20Suhani%20is%20the%20sole%20recipient%20in%20the%20category%20of%20Innovation%20and%20the%20only%20honoree%20from%20Delhi%20to%20receive%20this%20highest%20National%20Award%20for%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%202106px)%20100vw%2C%202106px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSuhani-Chauhan-with-Honble-Prime-Minister-Shri-Narendra-Modiji-and-Honble-Minister-for-Women-and-Child-Development-Smt.-Smriti-Irani-1_11zon-1732018716.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222106%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Suhani's%20interaction%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20was%20memorable%20for%20her%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSuhani-Chauhan-with-Honble-Prime-Minister-Shri-Narendra-Modiji-and-Honble-Minister-for-Women-and-Child-Development-Smt.-Smriti-Irani-1_11zon-1732018716.jpg%202106w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSuhani-Chauhan-with-Honble-Prime-Minister-Shri-Narendra-Modiji-and-Honble-Minister-for-Women-and-Child-Development-Smt.-Smriti-Irani-1_11zon-1732018716-300x181.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSuhani-Chauhan-with-Honble-Prime-Minister-Shri-Narendra-Modiji-and-Honble-Minister-for-Women-and-Child-Development-Smt.-Smriti-Irani-1_11zon-1732018716-500x301.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSuhani-Chauhan-with-Honble-Prime-Minister-Shri-Narendra-Modiji-and-Honble-Minister-for-Women-and-Child-Development-Smt.-Smriti-Irani-1_11zon-1732018716-768x462.jpg%20768w%2C%